column5: Heading up to the cottage on the west arm of nipissing this Wednesday evening.  Anyone fished the area lately??  Any french river reports would also be appreciated....upper french and middle...wolsely bay area....any musky coming out of these areas lately??  Any info would be appreciated   Cheers
